---
/**
 * USP dark section — 7 animated cards demonstrating ClearTax's continuous-compliance platform.
 * Ported from global-e-invoicing-mandate-page/index.html:1798-2122.
 *
 * IntersectionObserver triggers card animations (node-fade, bar fills, world bar, chart bars,
 * counter tickers) once the card enters the viewport.
 */
---

<section class="usp-dark-bg section-spacing">
  <div class="wf-container">
    <h2 class="usp-section-header">ClearTax is a <span class="primary-text">Continuous Compliance Platform</span></h2>
    <p class="usp-subheader">Enterprise-grade infrastructure trusted by the world's largest organizations</p>

    <div class="usp-grid">
      {/* card 1: Trusted Tax Data Warehouse */}
      <div class="usp-card">
        <h3 class="usp-card-title">Always-On e-Invoicing </h3>
        <p class="usp-card-description">Detects, diagnoses, and resubmits failed invoices automatically - no manual intervention, no AR disruption. Your invoices clear. Every time.</p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6093bce33d9b4bae841b04e3/69eb6c1e87029e32d83f9407_dummy-image.png" alt="Graphic placeholder" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* card 2: Faster Tax Operations */}
      <div class="usp-card">
        <h3 class="usp-card-title">Built for Your Busiest Day </h3>
        <p class="usp-card-description">10,000 e-invoices per second. Infrastructure that auto-scales as transactions grow. Month-end peaks. POS surges. Handled without a slowdown.</p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6093bce33d9b4bae841b04e3/69eb6c1e87029e32d83f9407_dummy-image.png" alt="Graphic placeholder" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* card 3: One System for The World */}
      <div class="usp-card">
        <h3 class="usp-card-title">Connects to Everything You Run On</h3>
        <p class="usp-card-description">SAP. Oracle. MS Dynamics. OMS. POS. Billing systems. All through pre-built, certified connectors.</p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6093bce33d9b4bae841b04e3/69eb6c1e87029e32d83f9407_dummy-image.png" alt="Graphic placeholder" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* card 4: Partner Ecosystem */}
      <div class="usp-card">
        <h3 class="usp-card-title">Zero Downtime. By Design. </h3>
        <p class="usp-card-description">A cloud outage never becomes a compliance gap. Your data stays in-country - wherever you operate. </p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6093bce33d9b4bae841b04e3/69eb6c1e87029e32d83f9407_dummy-image.png" alt="Graphic placeholder" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* card 5 (wide): Audit Ready */}
      <div class="usp-card usp-card-wide-2 usp-audit-ready-card">
        <h3 class="usp-card-title">One System for the World </h3>
        <p class="usp-card-description">50+ countries. One API. Switch on new country mandates with configuration, not code</p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6093bce33d9b4bae841b04e3/69eb6c1e87029e32d83f9407_dummy-image.png" alt="Graphic placeholder" class="w-full lg:max-w-[48%] h-auto rounded-lg" />
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* card 6 (wide): Enterprise AI Security */}
      <div class="usp-card usp-card-wide-2">
        <h3 class="usp-card-title">Enterprise AI Security</h3>
        <p class="usp-card-description usp-sec-row-content">SOC 2 Type II. ISO 27001:2022. AES 256-bit encryption at rest. Local data residency in every country you operate. Your data never leaves your environment and is never used to train models.</p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6093bce33d9b4bae841b04e3/69eb6c1e87029e32d83f9407_dummy-image.png" alt="Graphic placeholder" class="w-full lg:max-w-[48%] h-auto rounded-lg" />
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* card 7: Shield */}
      <div class="usp-card">
        <div class="usp-shield-content">
          <h3 class="usp-card-title">VAT Assurance: Recon AI Agent </h3>
          <p class="usp-card-description">Runs every day, automatically. Discrepancies are surfaced with AI-recommended actions. You're notified only when something needs your attention.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center">
          <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6093bce33d9b4bae841b04e3/69eb6c1e87029e32d83f9407_dummy-image.png" alt="Graphic placeholder" class="w-full" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style is:global>
  .usp-dark-bg { background: var(--color-white); }
  .section-spacing { padding: 100px 0; }
  /* .primary-text { color: #FFCF32; } */
  .wf-container { max-width: var(--container-max); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

  .usp-section-header { font-size: 44px; font-weight: 600; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 1.18; margin: 0; }
  .usp-subheader { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: black; text-align: center; margin-top: 16px; }

  .usp-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 28px; margin-top: 48px; }
  .usp-card { border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04); position: relative; }
  .usp-card:nth-child(odd) { background: #EDEBFA; }
  .usp-card:nth-child(even) { background: #FDF2ED; }

  /* Vertical contrast: Swapping colors for the last two cards to avoid stacking same colors */
  .usp-card:nth-last-child(2) { background: #EDEBFA; }
  .usp-card:nth-last-child(1) { background: #FDF2ED; }

  .usp-card-title { font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.36; font-weight: 500; color: black; margin: 0 0 12px; }
  .usp-card-description { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5; color: #000000CC; margin: 0; }
  .usp-card-wide-2 { grid-column: span 2; }

  @media (max-width: 1280px) {
    .usp-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .usp-card-wide-2 { grid-column: span 1; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .usp-section-header { font-size: 32px; }
    .usp-card { padding: 16px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .usp-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; width: 100%; }
    .usp-card { width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
